	<!-- message, attachments, sig -->
	<div class="alt2" style="margin:1px; padding:6px">
	
		
			<!-- icon and title -->
			<div class="smallfont">
				
				<strong>Shidima of Avalon Imperial Guards. lvl 52 Necro.</strong>
			</div>
			<hr size="1" color="#D1D1E1" />
			<!-- / icon and title -->
		
		
		<!-- message -->
		<div>I enter PoK with my lowbie alt and there was this lvl 52 Necro crying in /ooc about losing his corpse. When I sent him a tell he said that its under the world and that there are no GMs on to help him. I asked him if he tried summoning it, to which he replied that he didn't have the spell. <br />
<br />
So, I told him I could log my necro on and help him out. I told him I will summon it for him provided that he gives me a coffin upfront. He replied that he didn't have any money on him or on any other characters as this was his only character and that all the money he has is on his corpse. I told him the coffin costs 175 pp (PoK price with no cha item) and that I'll buy it provided that he'll repay me after I summon the corpse.<br />
<br />
So, I log Morguen on to buy the coffin and goes to Firiona Vie. His corpse was in firiona Vie and I summoned it for him. He looted his corpse after leaving an item on it for rezzing. He sat down after looting the corpse and waited for a while. I asked him if I can have my plat so I can log off. No reply from him still. He replied after five minutes of keeping me waiting, &quot;let me see how much a rez is going to cost me&quot;. He is in the meantime searching for a cleric while keeping me waiting.<br />
<br />
At that moment, I'm like.. ok.. I'm sure I'm not going to see the money. He owes me first, so he should have paid me first. A little while later a cleric from magister comes to rez him and didnt take any dontation for the rez. It was nice of her to do so.<br />
<br />
So, after he got the rez, he turns away from me.. sits down.. I'm starting to count the 30 seconds now.. and lo behold, hes logged off.<br />
<br />
This necro is level 52 necro named Shidima of Avalon Imperial Guards.<br />
<br />
Below are the screenshots of the conversation between Morguen and him. I don't have the screenshots of the conversation of my lowbie alt as I didnt think it was going to turn out this way.<br />
<br />
<a href="http://www.geocities.com/morguen_graves/shidimajpg.jpg" target="_blank">http://www.geocities.com/morguen_graves/shidimajpg.jpg</a><br />
<br />
The gnome necro Shidima.<br />
<br />
<a href="http://www.geocities.com/morguen_graves/shidimathenecro.jpg" target="_blank">http://www.geocities.com/morguen_gr...imathenecro.jpg</a><br />
<br />
All my EQ life i've only helped people out, many times going out of my way, to help someone in need. I think its about time I stopped doing it. Its sad to see people like him stabbing strangers in the back who go out of their way to help them. Its not the 175 pp that I've lost that I'm worried about. Its the sheer backstabbing of someone who went out of their way to help him. Sadly, the world is full of people like him.<br />
<br />
Morguen Graves<br />
51 Necromancer.</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
		
		
	
