		<div>Deref:  Back when the guild was first formed yes, just like any other.  Just as  I am sure your guild has a few not so nice peeps in it and has also been taken to the boards for some actions, not that its not a fine guild.  Also as you posted less than two hours from  the start of the thread I was trying to give a guild response as you thought there should be one.  In that post I apologised up front and offered to make good on the debt.  However I only had one side to go on at that time and was giving my reasons for not taking other actions at that point.<br />
